            GNOME SORT
            DIMENSION ARR(100)
            INTEGER I,N,TMP
            I=1
LOOP        WHENEVER I.G.N, TRANSFER TO DONE
            WHENEVER I.E.1.OR.ARR(I).GE.ARR(I-1), TRANSFER TO ADVANCE
            TMP=ARR(I)
            ARR(I)=ARR(I-1)
            ARR(I-1)=TMP
            I=I-1
            TRANSFER TO LOOP
ADVANCE     I=I+1
            TRANSFER TO LOOP
DONE        END OF FUNCTION
